    "Similarly, due attention is paid to the issues related to the control of the 'Electric power system' and 'System stability' implying the growing interest in increasing the efficiency of the wind energy systems when exposed to Fig. 14 Trending Topic on DFIG-based WECS Dynamic Analysiscertain types of dynamic operating conditions.",
    "This trend analysis further extends to point towards enhanced emphasis on quality and innovation in control of wind turbine systems as the world over adopts sustainable energy sources.",
    "Current trends in DFIG-based WECSDFIG-based WECS are widely used in wind power generation due to their advantages, such as high efficiency, low cost, and flexible control.",
